# Rumour Detection
It is a project to classify tweets as rumour or non-rumour

## Installation
First install libraries using requirement.txt file.
Run file run.linearcrfwithup.py to classify tweets. 
Possible parameters to be pass are given in run-linear-crf-content+social.sh and similar shell files.

Dataset is available in features folder which contains tweets event wise. 

## Reference
For better understanding of project read our research paper: https://authors.elsevier.com/c/1biw08nKGjCBPS

